title: Week 2 Waivers 2022
description:
Field Yates, Stephania Bell and Daniel Dopp recap a strange Monday Night Football game, talk the injuries you need to watch and what players have new expectations going forward. Plus, Eric Moody joins to tell us who to target on the waiver wire.
